Package com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.transport

Contains classes for communicating information between the services that are responsible for data access on-demand solutions in i2 Analyze.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExternalDataResults
    A result container that contains the requested Items, the ItemGroups that those Items and ItemPlaceholders belong to, and information about external sources from which results could not be retrieved.
    ExternalDataSubsetIdentifier
    A container for information that uniquely identifies a subset of data from an external data source.
    ItemGroup
    A container for information about a group of Items and ItemPlaceholders that appear in the results of a call to an external data retrieval or subset exploration service method.
    ProvenanceGroup
    A container for CardProvenances that are grouped together by a client-specified identifier.
    RetrievalBlockAvailability
    A container for information about the availability of external sources when a request for information from them was made.
    RetrievalBlockMapping
    A mapping that associates an Item (or an ItemPlaceholder) with a RetrievalBlock that was used to retrieve some of the data that the Item contains.
